name: Rhythm
description:
Rhythm is a set of nodes to help your Revit project maintain a good rhythm with Dynamo. Rhythm is fully open-source and authored by John Pierson (@johntpierson) of Design Tech Unraveled (designtechunraveled.com). 

Supported Revit versions are 2021-2024, with supported Dynamo versions being 2.6.x - 2.18.x
